Package: pohoda-abo-importer
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, php-cli, php-curl, php-json, php-xml, php-mbstring, composer
Architecture: all
Description: ABO bank statement importer for Pohoda accounting system
 A PHP application that imports ABO (bank statement) files into Pohoda 
 accounting software using mServer API. It parses ABO format bank statements 
 and creates bank movements in Pohoda with duplicate detection and error handling.
 .
 Features:
  * Parses ABO format bank statements using spojenet/abo-parser
  * Connects to Pohoda via mServer using vitexsoftware/pohoda-connector
  * Duplicate transaction detection and prevention
  * Comprehensive error handling and logging
  * JSON report generation with MultiFlexi schema compliance
  * Command-line interface with configurable options

Package: multiflexi-pohoda-abo-importer
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, pohoda-abo-importer, multiflexi
Architecture: all
Description: MultiFlexi integration for pohoda-abo-importer
 MultiFlexi application package for pohoda-abo-importer that enables
 integration with the MultiFlexi management system. Provides web-based
 configuration and monitoring capabilities for the ABO bank statement
 import process.
